-script test failover show thông tin như ip,...
-check đã backup đủ file hay chưa = cách gửi 1 file txt có chứa số lượng file được backup bên client, bên server kiểm tra số lượng qua file đó (done)
$path_backup/$date/$hostname_$ip/$services (tren server thi la /data/storage, tren client thi /data/backup) (done)
-ll -ltt (optional)
-motd (optional)
-encrypt folder khi backup cũng như restore
-chuyển file sử dụng rsync(port,custom user, passwd, ssh thi nên chi cho ket noi tu local toi cac container)
-crontab trong container 


viet demo.md


https://linuxize.com/post/scheduling-cron-jobs-with-crontab/

Run Cron Job Every Minute	* * * * * /root/backup.sh
Run Cron Job Every Day at Midnight	0 0 * * * /root/backup.sh
Run Cron Job Every Day at 0:5	5 0 * * * /root/backup.sh


https://linuxhint.com/encrypt-decrypt-with-pgp/
-encrypt dir chua compress file -> lb1.pgp -> khi giai nen se thanh lb1/
-transfer file do va store

gpg --gen-key
gpg --export -a tringo > public.key

gpg --output private.key --armor --export-secret-key tringo
gpg --output public.key --armor --export tringo


gpg --import public.key
gpg --import private.key

gpg --list-public-keys

gpg -e -r tringo --trust-model always test.txt

gpg --batch --passphrase 123123 test.txt.gpg



